></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"263\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:196.95pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;height:121.65pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Tüm<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n  2.0pt\"> </span>kategoriler<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>için<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>21<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>Kasım<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>2025 tarihinde sona eriyor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;height:106.4pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:67.1pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;\r\n  border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;height:106.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">39 (b) <span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n  -.1pt\">(27/11/2024</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-right:28.9pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\n  letter-spacing:-.1pt\">tarihli 2024/7</span><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"line-height:13.15pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;letter-spacing:-.1pt\">sayılı</span><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:.25pt;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Genelge<span style=\"letter-spacing:1.85pt\"> </